{
  "stem": "9963.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And that was [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] a camp between [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Till now, I was in labor camps.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But that was the first concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "The name was [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Szebnie. ?]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was not far from Krakow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was [INAUDIBLE] this is a-- a part of the ghetto of the-- what was the movie made?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Plaszow-- from Plaszow-- this was a part of Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The same commandant, Commandant Goeth, he was in charge of that camp, too.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Did you see the movie-- what was it?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You remember that Commandant Goeth?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was in Plaszow?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What I know about him I wish I wouldn't know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was a bad person, a very bad person.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I have bad names to call him, but I don't want to call him because I respect you as a lady, the names that I would call him, what he was.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What he did to people, it is just unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And for his own enjoyment, he'd murder people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He'd torture people, especially ladies.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He picked a young woman, and he tortured them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "What he did was unspeakable.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was-- three occasions, I was so close to him as I am from you on three occasions.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He came to that camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He picked, at one time, close to 2,000 people, took them in the woods, shot them all.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Then he took 18 people from camp with wood to burn them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They were burning day and night till they burned all the bodies.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon me?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The living conditions in that camp was barracks-- big barracks-- also about 300 people are living in a barrack.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the food was very, very little-- very little food.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The work was what we had to-- sorted merchandise.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
